2ee6f41e959a418f976dc4e:
  'Description': Identifies general problems or glitches in the device's
    display screen.
  'Skill Name': Display Problems
  'Entity':
  - 'Description': The brand of the phone experiencing display issues.
    'Attribute Identifier': f640ced21b2e4558a92edf3
    'Attribute Name': phone_brand
  - 'Description': The specific model of the phone experiencing display issues.
    'Attribute Identifier': 3b96c7f52d5f4700913cd36
    'Attribute Name': phone_model
  - 'Description': The type of display issue encountered on the phone.
    'Attribute Identifier': a77ca64f58374d3b8238eea
    'Attribute Name': display_issue
593e853a1224407f81520d7:
  'Description': Covers any difficulties or faults with the device's sound
    output.
  'Skill Name': Sound Problems
  'Entity':
  - 'Description': The specific model of the phone experiencing sound problems.
    'Attribute Identifier': 28826ab51a864618bb7b57e
    'Attribute Name': phone_model
  - 'Description': The type of sound problem being experienced.
    'Attribute Identifier': 5ceccc5b390a4d00a432901
    'Attribute Name': sound_issue
    'Similar values':
    - no sound
    - distorted sound
    - low volume
    - buzzing sound
    - crackling sound
  - 'Description': The specific sound component affected.
    'Attribute Identifier': bcd736e8088d4e27a8be915
    'Attribute Name': sound_component
c3f929fa702b42dd8bc6a17:
  'Description': Refers to the device's battery losing charge faster than
    expected, often due to background apps or screen brightness.
  'Skill Name': Battery Drain
  'Entity':
  - 'Description': The brand of the phone for which the battery drain is being
      diagnosed.
    'Attribute Identifier': 6fecabf50f5b41689ce5b45
    'Attribute Name': phone_brand
  - 'Description': The specific model of the phone for which the battery drain
      is being diagnosed.
    'Attribute Identifier': bf7aee4677974df1aa90e19
    'Attribute Name': phone_model
  - 'Description': The symptoms of the battery drain issue.
    'Attribute Identifier': e90feafde066409a8577aaf
    'Attribute Name': battery_drain_symptoms
caf80ccb6e7c45de9e03583:
  'Description': Describes any issues related to the device's battery life
    or performance.
  'Skill Name': Battery Problems
  'Entity':
  - 'Description': The brand of the phone having battery problems.
    'Attribute Identifier': b6e324bb8a974b5f9462510
    'Attribute Name': phone_brand
  - 'Description': The specific model of the phone having battery problems.
    'Attribute Identifier': 7e51c86ab4bd431d8f529d2
    'Attribute Name': phone_model
  - 'Description': The nature of the battery problem.
    'Attribute Identifier': 1e902eef8bca41f99020587
    'Attribute Name': battery_issue
